reached\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34032,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/03\/01\/refuge-physical-mental-illness\/","url_meta":{"origin":23570,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Disease: Seek refuge in Allah from physical, mental illness","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 1, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, would say, \u201cO Allah, I seek refuge in you from leprosy, madness, contagion, and evil ailments.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 1554 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Arna'ut \u064e\u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0633\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0645\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0650\u0643\u064d \u0623\u064e\u0646\u0651\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u064e \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u0643\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":5243,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/16\/tibb-every-disease-has-cure\/","url_meta":{"origin":23570,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Medicine: Allah created a cure for every disease","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 16, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud repo